data.description: Looking for space and a good price? Look no further! This Red Brick home sits on a large corner lot located in the heart of Leesburg. It features 3 bedrooms with 1 and 1/2 bathrooms and has 1699 heated and cooled square feet. Currently the Family room with the Fireplace is being used as a 4th bedroom. This home has lots of living space and an eat in kitchen. The Stainless Steel Appliances stay. The oversized yard is fenced in and has an above ground pool with a deck to enjoy on these warm Summer days. There is also a shed for extra storage. The screened in porch is nice for sitting outside enjoying your coffee or evening supper. Although the home needs some TLC you will not find a better home for the price. Schedule a Private Tour today! All information recorded in the MLS is intended to be accurate however, it should be independently verified by buyer and their agent.
